{"tid":743504,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"名偵探柯南,零之執行人,日本票房85億","createTime":"2018-07-15T12:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T09:22:11.000Z","uid":25345,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1f452f88ca9b8345c5c1ee72f35cb4cfc38adf81","tid":743504,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T12:45:50.000Z","msg":"名探偵コナン　ゼロの執行人 \t東宝 \t85.3億 \t2018/04/13<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79df60468e0629ef8d90d6e782c4db07104dae24","tid":743504,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"阿寶的威力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64d25fc5941d7c24436a4ec457617fc88b0fd425","tid":743504,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T12:49:24.000Z","msg":"全台熱映中的《名偵探柯南：零的執行人》，票房成長幅度驚人，完全延續了在日本上映的氣勢，不到一周，目前全台累績票房己近4千萬，刷新去年《唐紅的戀歌》的紀錄，更誇張的是己有人累計7刷了。同時，柯南在日本票房榜仍然榜上有名，截止上週日（7/8），《零的執行人》在日本上映的第13週，動員排行榜排名第8，累積票房共達85億2598萬2100日圓。可見柯南的威力十分強大，是柯南迷每年必定要朝聖的作品。<br />\n<br />\n本集票房熱燒持久不衰的原因是：本集的柯南製造不少的話題，尤其各個亮點都成功在電影院中讓觀眾發出讚嘆聲，在驚喜之下成功，讓觀眾跟著劇情一起高潮迭起。大量運用10T物聯網的手法製造許多案件爆發的不可思議，融合日本嚴謹的刑事系統警視廳、警察廳、檢察廳與各直屬公安的關係，在三大合作中隱藏許多角力，大家共同追求唯一的真相，但是追求的方式與執行正義的方法卻有無數種。究竟重要的是快速得知真相，還是貫徹正義呢?這次劇場版推理情節之細緻，讓人出乎意料，不到最後一刻無法察覺犯案兇手。<br />\n<br />\n《零的執行人》以降谷零(主角安室透的公安代號)之名出發，特別強調「零」的意義，0可以代表無也能代表有，連結與柯南和安室透在劇中一直找尋、渴望釐清的東西，這一場真相的追逐戰其實是證明價值的一場考驗。<br />\n<br />\n台灣都痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8e88e0a07747e9465bebcd0fe51c8b05a6f2594","tid":743504,"uid":10197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:05:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5890bb11a47ec67625f24260ffc4584d752490","tid":743504,"uid":150230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:16:18.000Z","msg":"日本唔係得幾億人渣咩"},{"pid":"d3136e0b9542de37ae49a7a98128b36f75de61b3","tid":743504,"uid":22018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6d96b02c00d79163020271221a80477fddb30b","tid":743504,"uid":73627,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:57:20.000Z","msg":"講個笑話<br />\n偵探"},{"pid":"b163b39c6139c2dd35d299ac0df2518096f12790","tid":743504,"uid":161731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"柯南係適合任何組合既人去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc27bda5900dd2f0c8e9b6c6f74c437add349ad","tid":743504,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"青山條撚樣肯定唔捨得結局啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774f88883289df471096cd32af20b1e3d69d68d8","tid":743504,"uid":128417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bc27bda5900dd2f0c8e9b6c6f74c437add349ad","tid":743504,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"青山條撚樣肯定唔捨得結局啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"就算青山想完<br />\n小學館都唔俾佢完"},{"pid":"b04a1e4e499aeb366b08906885103917225ff56c","tid":743504,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"774f88883289df471096cd32af20b1e3d69d68d8","tid":743504,"uid":128417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bc27bda5900dd2f0c8e9b6c6f74c437add349ad","tid":743504,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T15:08:24.000Z","msg":"青山條撚樣肯定唔捨得結局啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" cl